game.name: Elsa And Anna Wedding Party
game.description:
We have come up with great news from your favorite and charming frozen sisters! These beautiful princesses have found their love and today they both have decided to marry with these handsome hunks. Anna loves Kristoff and Elsa loves to tie a knot with Jack. But, their excitement level has made them confused what to put on to wear awesome on their special day. Do you dare to help these pairs of lovers to pick up the nice outfits? Join Elsa And Anna Wedding Party and get ready to enjoy their jointly hold wedding celebration!

You are playing the role of a wedding stylist in this brand new dressing game. Put your unique and sharp style sense and fashion abilities to the test to help princesses to become the most beautiful bride sisters! Go through all the wedding dress, hairstyle and make-up options and choose the ones that suit their look the most! Start with the make-up part and then give her a nice hairstyle and outfit! Choose a nice lipstick, and click the next button! Now mix and match all elegant gowns and combine them with a matching hairstyle, jewelry items and a pair of sandals in this html5 girls game. 

Once you are done with their make-up and wedding dresses, you have to take care of decorating their rooms. Put the nice wedding cake on the table, balloons and other gift items, flower pot and cupcakes. Make sure to use their wedding picture on the background and the ribbons on the top of the screen in this one of the best wedding games for kids. Congratulations! After completing this job, you will be ready to attend their wedding. Check out more fun princess games for girls that are free to play online, no download required on atmegame.com!
